I'm only working on this engine because i just enjoy making shit.
compile & run:
- src/main.c -
this is for testing object, universe, camera.
cd src && make uni

note: 
you will need to graphics
and sh bridge.sh then ./a.out before ^below^

execute: ./a.out 

- src/ff-lang.c -
firefly language.
cd src && make ffc

execute: ./ffc

- src/script.c -
firefly script
cd src && make script

execute: ./main

look for compile.sh as i use it to compile src/as, src/bond, etc

mechine: x86_64
OS: GNU/Linux - debian
version: Debian 4.9.82-1+deb9u3
